latestPosts.caption:
Makeup by @artistrybyresham 

As I worked on Krutika’s bridal makeup, I couldn’t help but feel grateful for the trust she’s placed in me. 

Krutika, you look breathtakingly beautiful, but it’s your love for each other that truly shines brighter than any makeup or adornment. 

Her journey is one for the fairy tales - reuniting with her middle-school sweetheart and now, exchanging vows to spend a lifetime together.

Thank you for allowing me to be a part of your special day. I’m honored to have played a small role in making your wedding day dreams come true.
